|6 |          ├─SUBPLAN SCAN         |VIEW2       |12      |15          |
|7 |          │ └─MERGE JOIN         |            |12      |15          |
|8 |          │   ├─SORT             |            |17      |7           |
|9 |          │   │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN|CHILD1      |17      |4           |
|10|          │   └─TABLE FULL SCAN  |PARENT1     |34      |5           |
|11|          └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |GRANDPARENT1|13      |5           |
